{"tid":808634,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtuber嚟講，小玉都幾乞人憎","createTime":"2018-09-06T13:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T13:37:32.000Z","uid":93046,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"48d9a138382907dd7ee21818ed5ac49f99a098ba","tid":808634,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:12:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t69mjpyQo1E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft69mjpyQo1E&d=33ZlhKVvrwGLRFUT9hC9CdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=18056d54\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t69mjpyQo1E</a><br />\n<br />\n三更半夜去人地舖頭搗亂，<br />\n表情又猙獰，<br />\n講嘢煩同嘈<br />\n<br />\n人地Hajime 社長炫富，起碼佢冇影響到人<br />\n佢炫富，只會令人覺得佢好乞人憎<br />\n雖然佢不嬲都係煩膠，但自從佢啲訂閱數多過佢細佬，佢就好似走火入魔咁。<br />\n<br />\n仲有條片後面又有啲懶感性說話，都唔知佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扮晒懷才不遇咁"},{"pid":"05f1dbdc53a5a4a7a29bb4d0b4a6a7e40a9b5b54","tid":808634,"uid":115441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"台灣youtube界小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣d創作者其實質素好參差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54456f383856900af6da7b871f4b395368f204c","tid":808634,"uid":153570,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"個樣真心衰"},{"pid":"79db567884a49421d02746a981b8413555b807f5","tid":808634,"uid":93046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eQ0hHhtPWWI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeQ0hHhtPWWI&d=33ZlhKVvrwGLRFUT9hC9CdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ff471dac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eQ0hHhtPWWI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片係後續，話說上面條片<br />\n佢俾便利店投訴未經批准拍攝<br />\n所以條片被強制下架<br />\n<br />\n呢條可以話係佢嘅道歉片<br />\n但一啲歉意都冇，仲要假喊<br />\n條片仲要開廣告賺錢<br />\n呢個人真係好厚面皮"},{"pid":"99722b46223c10fef910dfb678879783312f4914","tid":808634,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"條西面肥婆同佢相映成趣"},{"pid":"062dac0f2945279a6ad7e39d99db03c686fe5dbd","tid":808634,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做埋啲標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明三萬幾邊有用十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f8f9ce6932be8dedba593cadf379bf0075faf8","tid":808634,"uid":93046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"062dac0f2945279a6ad7e39d99db03c686fe5dbd","tid":808634,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做埋啲標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明三萬幾邊有用十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"7000幾蚊港紙都好攞出嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd28f268cd899c9fd6f57a3e6ddef9d864490a26","tid":808634,"uid":171594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"佢啲片一啲養分都冇<br />\n台灣人本身冇腦先做就到呢類youtuber發達"},{"pid":"c4fdb5c5232c57a71b132c2670918a9f64b0a715","tid":808634,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:37:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}